# No tooling branding

- Never add footers, trailers, badges, or visible text such as "Made with Cursor", "MADE WITH CURSOR", or similar editor/IDE attribution to UI, HTML, README, or comments unless the user explicitly asks for it.
- Do not add hidden metadata or strings whose only purpose is to credit the coding tool.
